Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:26.56,英文,,0,0,0,,Alright, so I'm Circle Chen, I'm from China, and this is my sixth time TAing for this course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:26.56,中文,,0,0,0,,好的  我是Circle  来自中国  这是我第六次担任这门课程的助教
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.56,0:04:28.72,英文,,0,0,0,,And I love all things game-related.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.56,0:04:28.72,中文,,0,0,0,,我喜欢所有与游戏相关的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.72,0:04:31.80,英文,,0,0,0,,I also play game music at the Intermission Orchestra.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.72,0:04:31.80,中文,,0,0,0,,我还在 Intermission Orchestra 乐团演奏游戏音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.80,0:04:38.81,英文,,0,0,0,,I have my itch profile, these are some of my games I made.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.80,0:04:38.81,中文,,0,0,0,,这是我的 itch 个人资料  上面展示了我制作的一些游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:47.67,英文,,0,0,0,,So today we're going to cover game development.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:47.67,中文,,0,0,0,,今天我们将讨论游戏开发
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.67,0:04:52.37,英文,,0,0,0,,And specifically indie game development.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.67,0:04:52.37,中文,,0,0,0,,特别是独立游戏开发
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.37,0:04:58.49,英文,,0,0,0,,If we think about what we did in the introductory CS courses, these actually all involve some sort of game building.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.37,0:04:58.49,中文,,0,0,0,,如果我们回顾一下我们在 CS 入门课程中所做的内容  这些实际上都涉及某种游戏构建
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.49,0:05:00.49,英文,,0,0,0,,In 61A, you did the game Hog.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.49,0:05:00.49,中文,,0,0,0,,在 61A 中  你们做了 Hog 游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.49,0:05:02.45,英文,,0,0,0,,It's like a game of dice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.49,0:05:02.45,中文,,0,0,0,,这就像一个骰子游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.45,0:05:05.97,英文,,0,0,0,,We did Ants. It's like a Planet vs. Zombie copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.45,0:05:05.97,中文,,0,0,0,,我们做了 Ants 游戏   它就像一个植物大战僵尸的副本
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.97,0:05:12.32,英文,,0,0,0,,In 61B, we built these two games, 2048 and Build Your Own World.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.97,0:05:12.32,中文,,0,0,0,,在 61B 中  我们构建了这两个游戏：2048 和 Build Your Own World(BYOW)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.32,0:05:14.84,英文,,0,0,0,,Now, you might wonder, why do we do games?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.32,0:05:14.84,中文,,0,0,0,,现在  你可能会想  为什么我们要做游戏呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.84,0:05:18.02,英文,,0,0,0,,Why is game development always so crucial?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.84,0:05:18.02,中文,,0,0,0,,为什么游戏开发总是如此重要？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.02,0:05:26.67,英文,,0,0,0,,We do these because games are fun, and we hope that the pleasure of implementing a game is actually going to be a motivation for you to learn programming further.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.02,0:05:26.67,中文,,0,0,0,,我们这样做是因为游戏很有趣  我们希望实现游戏的乐趣能够真正激励你进一步学习编程
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.67,0:05:31.71,英文,,0,0,0,,So that's why we give you assignments that are on games.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.67,0:05:31.71,中文,,0,0,0,,这就是为什么我们给你们的作业都是关于游戏的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.71,0:05:41.82,英文,,0,0,0,,Now, let's say some of you, after you're finished with all the game building, think about, okay, what if I want to take a step forward and make this a hobby?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.71,0:05:41.82,中文,,0,0,0,,现在  假设你们中的一些人  在完成了所有的游戏构建之后  想更进一步  把它作为一种爱好  会怎么样呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.82,0:05:46.72,英文,,0,0,0,,Some of you then, indie game development might be a good fit for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.82,0:05:46.72,中文,,0,0,0,,那么对于你们中的一些人来说  独立游戏开发可能是一个不错的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.72,0:05:50.06,英文,,0,0,0,,This is what I'm going to discuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.72,0:05:50.06,中文,,0,0,0,,我要讨论的就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.06,0:05:53.68,英文,,0,0,0,,The word indie here means independent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.06,0:05:53.68,中文,,0,0,0,,这里的“独立”是指独立开发者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.68,0:06:00.54,英文,,0,0,0,,This will be contrast as if you're working with game companies like Blizzard or Riot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.68,0:06:00.54,中文,,0,0,0,,这与在暴雪或拳头游戏公司工作形成对比
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:09.93,英文,,0,0,0,,There's a lot more freedom you can do, but it can still be very demanding because you need to set your own deadlines and manage your own work schedule.
