Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.70,0:23:32.26,英文,,0,0,0,,So we're going to discuss the pipelines of making a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.70,0:23:32.26,中文,,0,0,0,,所以我们将讨论制作游戏的流程
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.26,0:23:36.16,英文,,0,0,0,,And let's say you designed those game mechanics like the ones you mentioned above.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.26,0:23:36.16,中文,,0,0,0,,假设你设计了像上面提到的那些游戏机制
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.16,0:23:39.39,英文,,0,0,0,,How would you actually turn it into a final product?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.16,0:23:39.39,中文,,0,0,0,,你将如何把它变成最终产品？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.39,0:23:42.35,英文,,0,0,0,,Now, you'll need to work with a lot of different people on your team.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.39,0:23:42.35,中文,,0,0,0,,现在  你需要和团队中的许多不同的人一起工作
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.35,0:23:46.79,英文,,0,0,0,,You're going to be working with designers, artists, or musicians.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.35,0:23:46.79,中文,,0,0,0,,你将与设计师、艺术家或音乐家合作
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.79,0:23:50.65,英文,,0,0,0,,And you're going to be working with other programmers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.79,0:23:50.65,中文,,0,0,0,,你将与其他程序员合作
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.65,0:23:55.66,英文,,0,0,0,,And you're going to be working with testers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.65,0:23:55.66,中文,,0,0,0,,你将与测试人员合作
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.66,0:24:01.28,英文,,0,0,0,,And there's also a timeline for starting from a game and making it an actual thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.66,0:24:01.28,中文,,0,0,0,,从游戏开始到把它变成一个实际的东西  还有一个时间表
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.28,0:24:11.77,英文,,0,0,0,,So you're going to start with an idea, and then you're going to create paper prototypes, and then you create a minimum viable product, abbreviated as MVP.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.28,0:24:11.77,中文,,0,0,0,,所以你将从一个想法开始  然后创建纸质原型  然后创建一个最小可行产品  缩写为MVP
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.77,0:24:17.77,英文,,0,0,0,,And then you iteratively improve your game by going through alpha, beta, and release.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.77,0:24:17.77,中文,,0,0,0,,然后  你通过经历α、β和发布来迭代地改进你的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.77,0:24:27.11,英文,,0,0,0,,So I'll just explain using Minecraft as an example, but the general process should be the same no matter what game you're looking into.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.77,0:24:27.11,中文,,0,0,0,,所以我将以《我的世界》为例进行解释  但无论你看的是什么游戏  一般的过程都应该是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.11,0:24:31.45,英文,,0,0,0,,So the ideation phase is a couple sentences or elements relevant to the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.11,0:24:31.45,中文,,0,0,0,,因此  构思阶段是与游戏相关的几句话或元素
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.45,0:24:36.36,英文,,0,0,0,,And for Minecraft, this includes some of these rationales.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.45,0:24:36.36,中文,,0,0,0,,对于《我的世界》来说  这包括以下一些原理
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.36,0:24:38.62,英文,,0,0,0,,So for Build Your Own World, it's actually kind of similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.36,0:24:38.62,中文,,0,0,0,,所以对于“建造你自己的世界”来说  它实际上有点类似
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.62,0:24:46.28,英文,,0,0,0,,The idea is like randomly generate a world with rooms and hallways, and you have an avatar that can move.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.62,0:24:46.28,中文,,0,0,0,,这个想法就像是随机生成一个包含房间和走廊的世界  然后你有一个可以移动的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.28,0:24:49.84,英文,,0,0,0,,Now, this is one of the games Minecraft is inspired by.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.28,0:24:49.84,中文,,0,0,0,,这是《我的世界》灵感来源的游戏之一
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.84,0:24:50.95,英文,,0,0,0,,It's called Infant Miner.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.84,0:24:50.95,中文,,0,0,0,,它叫做《矮人矿工》
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.95,0:24:55.12,英文,,0,0,0,,You have block-based worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.95,0:24:55.12,中文,,0,0,0,,它拥有方块构成的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.12,0:24:56.73,英文,,0,0,0,,Now we then have a paper prototype.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.12,0:24:56.73,中文,,0,0,0,,然后我们会有一个纸上原型
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.73,0:25:01.71,英文,,0,0,0,,So basically, this just presents the game on paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.73,0:25:01.71,中文,,0,0,0,,基本上  这只是将游戏呈现在纸上
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.71,0:25:08.75,英文,,0,0,0,,And then the purpose of this is just for people to discuss all the ideas, and they can make changes quickly without actually writing any code.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.71,0:25:08.75,中文,,0,0,0,,这样做的目的是让人们可以讨论所有的想法  并且可以快速地进行更改  而无需实际编写任何代码
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.75,0:25:12.62,英文,,0,0,0,,Because when you write code, you debug them, and changes take a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.75,0:25:12.62,中文,,0,0,0,,因为当你写代码的时候  你需要调试它们  而且修改需要花费很长时间
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.62,0:25:18.20,英文,,0,0,0,,But if you write stuff in paper, you can just erase it and write up new stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.62,0:25:18.20,中文,,0,0,0,,但是如果你把东西写在纸上  你就可以直接擦掉它  然后写上新的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.20,0:25:22.64,英文,,0,0,0,,So here are some example paper prototypes from the game Binding of Isaac.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.20,0:25:22.64,中文,,0,0,0,,这里有一些来自游戏《以撒的结合》的纸上原型的例子
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.64,0:25:25.37,英文,,0,0,0,,I don't think there are any Minecraft paper prototypes lying out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.64,0:25:25.37,中文,,0,0,0,,我不认为有任何《我的世界》的纸上原型流传在外
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.37,0:25:29.29,英文,,0,0,0,,So you're going to actually think about one, two, three.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.37,0:25:29.29,中文,,0,0,0,,所以你要实际考虑一下  一  二  三
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.29,0:25:31.87,英文,,0,0,0,,What are the main mechanics?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.29,0:25:31.87,中文,,0,0,0,,主要的机制是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.87,0:25:38.67,英文,,0,0,0,,And you can change them if you just think those are not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.87,0:25:38.67,中文,,0,0,0,,如果你觉得那些不好  你可以改变它们
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.67,0:25:46.94,英文,,0,0,0,,And then after a paper prototype, we'll actually be going into the MVP stage, where we develop a bare bones but still playable version of the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.67,0:25:46.94,中文,,0,0,0,,在纸上原型之后  我们会进入MVP阶段  在这个阶段  我们会开发一个基本但仍然可以玩的版本的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.94,0:25:52.25,英文,,0,0,0,,So the purpose is to tell others that the idea works because it's been implemented into code.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.94,0:25:52.25,中文,,0,0,0,,这样做的目的是告诉别人这个想法是可行的  因为它已经被实现成代码了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.25,0:25:55.83,英文,,0,0,0,,And this is what the MVP for Minecraft looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.25,0:25:55.83,中文,,0,0,0,,这就是《我的世界》的MVP的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.83,0:26:01.19,英文,,0,0,0,,It's actually the earliest playable version of Minecraft you can see, but it's very bare bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.83,0:26:01.19,中文,,0,0,0,,这是你能看到的《我的世界》最早的可玩版本  但它非常简陋
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.19,0:26:05.00,英文,,0,0,0,,There are no other enemies, but there are just like these blocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.19,0:26:05.00,中文,,0,0,0,,没有其他敌人  只有这些方块
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.00,0:26:14.27,英文,,0,0,0,,And as a note, given the time we give you on Build Your Own World, your game will likely top up at this stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.00,0:26:14.27,中文,,0,0,0,,请注意  考虑到我们在“构建你自己的世界”中给你的时间  你的游戏很可能会在这个阶段结束
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.27,0:26:15.23,英文,,0,0,0,,And then we have Alpha.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.27,0:26:15.23,中文,,0,0,0,,然后是 Alpha 版本
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.23,0:26:21.12,英文,,0,0,0,,So the purpose of Alpha is to show the game to a larger audience, including maybe your friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.23,0:26:21.12,中文,,0,0,0,,Alpha 版本的目的是向更广泛的受众展示游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.12,0:26:28.12,英文,,0,0,0,,maybe other people you don't know, and then have them just do a playtest and receive feedback.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.12,0:26:28.12,中文,,0,0,0,,比如你的朋友或者你不认识的人  让他们进行游戏测试并收集反馈
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.12,0:26:33.65,英文,,0,0,0,,So this is Alpha Minecraft, still missing a lot of the real features from the game,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.12,0:26:33.65,中文,,0,0,0,,这是 Alpha 版的 Minecraft  它仍然缺少很多正式版的功能
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.65,0:26:39.65,英文,,0,0,0,,but you see we have trees, we have more advanced things from the base game.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.65,0:26:39.65,中文,,0,0,0,,但你能看到我们有树  还有比基础版更高级的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.65,0:26:44.42,英文,,0,0,0,,And then we have beta, and this will be a preliminary release to the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.65,0:26:44.42,中文,,0,0,0,,然后是 Beta 版本  这将是面向公众的初步发布版本
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.42,0:26:50.99,英文,,0,0,0,,So in alpha, your share circle is limited to some people who you know, but if you're doing beta,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.42,0:26:50.99,中文,,0,0,0,,在 Alpha 版本中  你的分享范围仅限于你认识的一些人  但如果是 Beta 版本
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.99,0:26:57.99,英文,,0,0,0,,then you might just post the link online, then people who don't know you would just click on that link and play the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.99,0:26:57.99,中文,,0,0,0,,你可能会直接将链接发布到网上  那么不认识你的人也可以点击链接并玩游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.99,0:27:04.43,英文,,0,0,0,,And then you see you have more varied biomes in Minecraft, and you have other fancy stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.99,0:27:04.43,中文,,0,0,0,,然后你会看到 Minecraft 中有更多样化的生物群系  还有其他一些很酷的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.43,0:27:11.99,英文,,0,0,0,,And then for full release, full release is just at some point you decide that you don't want this game to be in beta anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.43,0:27:11.99,中文,,0,0,0,,至于正式版  就是指你决定不再让这个游戏处于 Beta 阶段的某个时间点
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.99,0:27:16.10,英文,,0,0,0,,You just want to announce to the public that this game is an official game.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.99,0:27:16.10,中文,,0,0,0,,你想向公众宣布这款游戏是正式版了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.10,0:27:18.10,英文,,0,0,0,,And the cutoff can be a little bit blurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.10,0:27:18.10,中文,,0,0,0,,而这个界限可能有点模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.10,0:27:24.36,英文,,0,0,0,,You can decide at some point, maybe you want to finalize the game details more, so you just put off.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.10,0:27:24.36,中文,,0,0,0,,你可以在某个时候决定  也许你想进一步完善游戏细节  所以你推迟了正式发布
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.36,0:27:28.80,英文,,0,0,0,,Or you could just do it early and then release version updates.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.36,0:27:28.80,中文,,0,0,0,,或者你也可以早点发布  然后发布版本更新
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.80,0:27:35.14,英文,,0,0,0,,So for Minecraft, this is when you can beat the Ender Dragon and beat the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.80,0:27:35.14,中文,,0,0,0,,对于 Minecraft 来说  这就是你可以击败末影龙并通关游戏的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.14,0:27:41.34,英文,,0,0,0,,After the final release, the game is still under active development, and it still receives updates.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.14,0:27:41.34,中文,,0,0,0,,在正式版发布后  游戏仍在积极开发中  并且仍然会收到更新
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.34,0:27:49.11,英文,,0,0,0,,When I started playing Minecraft, it was 1.4.7, but now it's already 1.20-something, and it's still going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.34,0:27:49.11,中文,,0,0,0,,当我开始玩 Minecraft 时  版本是 1.4.7  但现在已经是 1.20 多了  而且还在继续更新
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.11,0:27:52.91,英文,,0,0,0,,You can see the game is not a static product.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.11,0:27:52.91,中文,,0,0,0,,你可以看到游戏不是一个静态的产品
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.91,0:27:58.49,英文,,0,0,0,,It's something that you'll build down more and more.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.91,0:27:58.49,中文,,0,0,0,,它是你会不断完善的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.49,0:28:03.10,英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and we'll shift gears briefly into programmer perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.49,0:28:03.10,中文,,0,0,0,,是的  我们将简要地从程序员的角度来探讨一下
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.10,0:28:07.00,英文,,0,0,0,,But just before that, if anyone has any questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.10,0:28:07.00,中文,,0,0,0,,但在那之前  如果有人有任何问题的话
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.00,0:28:15.10,英文,,0,0,0,,Let's see, do we have any questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.00,0:28:15.10,中文,,0,0,0,,我们看看  有没有什么问题？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.10,0:28:16.58,英文,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.10,0:28:16.58,中文,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.58,0:28:19.46,英文,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.58,0:28:19.46,中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.46,0:28:24.57,英文,,0,0,0,,Okay, we'll be going on the programming stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.46,0:28:24.57,中文,,0,0,0,,好的  我们接下来讲编程方面的内容
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.57,0:28:30.97,英文,,0,0,0,,So we talked about how games are made in general, like the pipeline things, but we didn't really talk about how we actually code them.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.57,0:28:30.97,中文,,0,0,0,,我们之前讨论了游戏制作的总体流程  但没有具体讨论如何编写代码
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.97,0:28:37.64,英文,,0,0,0,,And this is actually what it's more relevant to like 62MB, because 62MB is like a data structure, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.97,0:28:37.64,中文,,0,0,0,,这和 62MB 比较相关  因为 62MB 本身就是一种数据结构
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.64,0:28:46.16,英文,,0,0,0,,So let's say the problem that we currently have is we want to design a build your own world with encounters, similar to encounter systems in Pokemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.64,0:28:46.16,中文,,0,0,0,,假设我们现在的目标是设计一个“建造自己的世界”游戏  其中包含类似于《精灵宝可梦》的遭遇系统
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.16,0:28:48.15,英文,,0,0,0,,So this is the Pokemon world.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.16,0:28:48.15,中文,,0,0,0,,这是《精灵宝可梦》的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.15,0:28:55.43,英文,,0,0,0,,It looks kind of like a build your own world, but What an encounter looks like is this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.15,0:28:55.43,中文,,0,0,0,,它看起来有点像“建造自己的世界”  但是... 遭遇战是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.43,0:28:59.35,英文,,0,0,0,,Let's say you're walking randomly and then you trigger, it's kind of like a step on landmine thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.43,0:28:59.35,中文,,0,0,0,,假设你随机走动  然后触发了遭遇战  有点像踩到地雷一样
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.35,0:29:06.40,英文,,0,0,0,,You suddenly enter into a battle and then some wild monsters appear and you need to engage and battle with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.35,0:29:06.40,中文,,0,0,0,,你突然进入战斗  一些野生怪物出现  你需要与它们战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.40,0:29:11.18,英文,,0,0,0,,So we're going to think about how we can implement this.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.40,0:29:11.18,中文,,0,0,0,,所以我们要考虑如何实现这个功能
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.18,0:29:19.26,英文,,0,0,0,,So if we recall how the basic build run works because we want to build our foundations, you would do this in a while loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.18,0:29:19.26,中文,,0,0,0,,如果我们回顾一下基本的构建运行原理  因为我们想构建基础  你会在一个 while 循环中进行操作
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.26,0:29:25.97,英文,,0,0,0,,So process input, update universe, and render the current state to the user.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.26,0:29:25.97,中文,,0,0,0,,流程是：处理输入、更新世界状态  然后将当前状态渲染给用户
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.97,0:29:35.85,英文,,0,0,0,,Now you also want to wait a little bit until the next update because you want the game maybe run at 60 frames per second or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.97,0:29:35.85,中文,,0,0,0,,你还要等待一段时间直到下一次更新  因为你可能希望游戏以每秒 60 帧的速度运行
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.85,0:29:40.16,英文,,0,0,0,,Now about keeping the code clean,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.85,0:29:40.16,中文,,0,0,0,,关于保持代码整洁
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.16,0:29:47.56,英文,,0,0,0,,So in our Build Your Own World with Encounters, there are actually different scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.16,0:29:47.56,中文,,0,0,0,,在我们的“建造自己的世界”游戏中  实际上有不同的场景
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.56,0:29:49.66,英文,,0,0,0,,You start at the main menu.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.56,0:29:49.66,中文,,0,0,0,,你从主菜单开始
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.66,0:29:53.25,英文,,0,0,0,,When you press N, you go to the Enter Scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.66,0:29:53.25,中文,,0,0,0,,当你按下 N 键时  你进入输入场景
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.25,0:29:56.41,英文,,0,0,0,,And then when you press S, you go to the World Scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.25,0:29:56.41,中文,,0,0,0,,然后当你按下 S 键时  你进入世界场景
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.41,0:30:00.55,英文,,0,0,0,,And then at some point, you randomly go into the Encounters Scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.41,0:30:00.55,中文,,0,0,0,,然后在某个时刻  你会随机进入遭遇战场景
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.55,0:30:05.03,英文,,0,0,0,,So the problem is that each scene will have different things to update.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.55,0:30:05.03,中文,,0,0,0,,问题是每个场景都需要更新不同的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.03,0:30:12.91,英文,,0,0,0,,So if you're in the world scene, you render blocks and process WSD, but if you're in the encounter scene,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.03,0:30:12.91,中文,,0,0,0,,例如  在世界场景中  你需要渲染块并处理WSD  但在遭遇场景中
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.91,0:30:20.91,英文,,0,0,0,,you don't want to render the world tiles because they're just not in the encounter, but you want to render the information that's pertinent to the encounter.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.91,0:30:20.91,中文,,0,0,0,,你不想渲染世界瓦片  因为它们不在遭遇中  而你想渲染与遭遇相关的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.91,0:30:27.98,英文,,0,0,0,,So let's revisit our requirements given that we've solved those constraints.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.91,0:30:27.98,中文,,0,0,0,,既然我们已经解决了这些限制  让我们重新审视一下我们的需求
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.98,0:30:32.82,英文,,0,0,0,,We want to make the game do different things in different scenes correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.98,0:30:32.82,中文,,0,0,0,,我们希望游戏在不同的场景中正确地做不同的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.82,0:30:40.32,英文,,0,0,0,,And we also want to enable us so that adding new scenes should be relatively easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.82,0:30:40.32,中文,,0,0,0,,我们也希望能够相对容易地添加新场景
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.32,0:30:45.52,英文,,0,0,0,,That means you should code in a clean way so that you won't hate your past self.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.32,0:30:45.52,中文,,0,0,0,,这意味着你应该用简洁的方式编码  这样你就不会讨厌过去的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.52,0:30:47.11,英文,,0,0,0,,So how can we do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.52,0:30:47.11,中文,,0,0,0,,那么我们该如何做到这一点呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.11,0:30:59.01,英文,,0,0,0,,I'll actually show people two solutions that are attempts but have some shortcomings, and then I'll give a solution that's, to my understanding, pretty clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.11,0:30:59.01,中文,,0,0,0,,我将向大家展示两种尝试性的解决方案  但都有一些缺点  然后我会提供一个在我看来非常简洁的解决方案
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.01,0:31:01.65,英文,,0,0,0,,So this is the first thing that we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.01,0:31:01.65,中文,,0,0,0,,这是我们的第一个方案
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.65,0:31:04.29,英文,,0,0,0,,We're going to have nested while loops.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.65,0:31:04.29,中文,,0,0,0,,我们将使用嵌套的 while 循环
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.29,0:31:06.66,英文,,0,0,0,,This could be abstracted as their own function.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.29,0:31:06.66,中文,,0,0,0,,这可以抽象为它们自己的函数
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.66,0:31:08.60,英文,,0,0,0,,I could have a title screen that has a while loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.66,0:31:08.60,中文,,0,0,0,,我可以有一个标题屏幕  它有一个 while 循环
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.60,0:31:10.80,英文,,0,0,0,,I could have an enter seed that's a while loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.60,0:31:10.80,中文,,0,0,0,,我可以有一个输入种子的 while 循环
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.80,0:31:14.28,英文,,0,0,0,,I could have a world movement that's a while loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.80,0:31:14.28,中文,,0,0,0,,我可以有一个世界移动的 while 循环
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.28,0:31:19.84,英文,,0,0,0,,But something that we don't like about this if you want to create a new scene,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.28,0:31:19.84,中文,,0,0,0,,但我们不喜欢这种方式的一点是如果你想创建一个新场景
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.84,0:31:25.96,英文,,0,0,0,,you're going to add another nested wild over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.84,0:31:25.96,中文,,0,0,0,,你就要在这里添加另一个嵌套的 while 循环
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.96,0:31:31.76,英文,,0,0,0,,This hurts the readability, because the more you indent, the more complicated your code becomes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.96,0:31:31.76,中文,,0,0,0,,这损害了代码的可读性  因为缩进越多  代码就越复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.76,0:31:47.16,英文,,0,0,0,,Actually, it's not possible to switch back and forth between three scenes using these, because you couldn't just ignore that and then go to the outermost immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.76,0:31:47.16,中文,,0,0,0,,实际上  使用这些方法不可能在三个场景之间来回切换  因为你不能简单地忽略它  然后立即跳转到最外层
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.16,0:31:50.75,英文,,0,0,0,,Now, here's a better approach, but it could still be improved.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.16,0:31:50.75,中文,,0,0,0,,现在  这是一个更好的方法  但仍然可以改进
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.75,0:31:56.93,英文,,0,0,0,,Let's say I have a string variable that represents the current state, and then I just put all these if-else branches to check
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.75,0:31:56.93,中文,,0,0,0,,假设我有一个字符串变量来表示当前状态  然后我只需将所有这些 if-else 分支放在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.93,0:32:01.93,英文,,0,0,0,,what is the current scene, and I just do different things accordingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.93,0:32:01.93,中文,,0,0,0,,以检查当前场景是什么  然后相应地做不同的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.93,0:32:08.56,英文,,0,0,0,,Now, for people in the chat or maybe this audience, what is something that could be improved about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.93,0:32:08.56,中文,,0,0,0,,对于聊天室或现场观众来说  有什么地方可以改进的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.56,0:32:17.83,英文,,0,0,0,,Or what is something that's not optimal about this code, or not clean?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.56,0:32:17.83,中文,,0,0,0,,或者说  这段代码有什么地方不够优化  或者不够简洁？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.83,0:32:23.51,英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah, exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.83,0:32:23.51,中文,,0,0,0,,是的  没错
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.51,0:32:28.85,英文,,0,0,0,,You do like a bunch of different equal checks every time, and just to elaborate a little bit on that, let's say you want to add a new scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.51,0:32:28.85,中文,,0,0,0,,每次你都要做一堆不同的相等检查  为了更详细地说明这一点  假设你想添加一个新的场景
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.85,0:32:29.63,英文,,0,0,0,,What would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.85,0:32:29.63,中文,,0,0,0,,你会怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.63,0:32:33.25,英文,,0,0,0,,What would you need to do here?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.63,0:32:33.25,中文,,0,0,0,,你需要在这里做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.25,0:32:38.52,英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you need to add another statement, and that's something we kind of don't want
