Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.38,0:39:37.78,英文,,0,0,0,,Now, based on the discussion from Java, like you've seen before, coding games from scratch is really hard because it requires code that exists in most games.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.38,0:39:37.78,中文,,0,0,0,,基于之前Java的讨论  你们也看到了  从头开始编写游戏代码真的很困难  因为它需要在大多数游戏中都存在的代码
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.78,0:39:47.45,英文,,0,0,0,,Like the scene transition thing, you're probably gonna think about like, okay, because you have so many different games that have scene transition, you're probably gonna have all the repeated code.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.78,0:39:47.45,中文,,0,0,0,,就像场景转换的东西  你可能会想  好吧  因为你有很多不同的游戏都有场景转换  你可能会重复所有的代码
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.45,0:39:53.09,英文,,0,0,0,,Can we just somehow abstract away all those redundant code, also called boilerplate?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.45,0:39:53.09,中文,,0,0,0,,我们能不能以某种方式抽象出所有这些冗余的代码  也称为样板代码？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.09,0:39:55.41,英文,,0,0,0,,And the answer is game engines.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.09,0:39:55.41,中文,,0,0,0,,答案就是游戏引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.41,0:39:58.04,英文,,0,0,0,,So one example is called Unity.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.41,0:39:58.04,中文,,0,0,0,,举个例子  叫做Unity
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.04,0:40:02.80,英文,,0,0,0,,Unity is abstracted so well that you could develop games codelessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.04,0:40:02.80,中文,,0,0,0,,Unity被抽象得很好  你可以不用写代码就开发游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.80,0:40:08.80,英文,,0,0,0,,In Unity, everything that exists in a game is called a GameObject.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.80,0:40:08.80,中文,,0,0,0,,在Unity中  游戏中存在的所有东西都称为GameObject（游戏对象）
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.80,0:40:14.77,英文,,0,0,0,,You can download GameObjects made by others, and you can drag and drop the objects in the Unity editor.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.80,0:40:14.77,中文,,0,0,0,,你可以下载别人制作的GameObjects  并将其拖放到Unity编辑器中
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.77,0:40:19.07,英文,,0,0,0,,This is an example of a LEGO blocks world.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.77,0:40:19.07,中文,,0,0,0,,这是一个乐高积木世界的例子
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.07,0:40:27.42,英文,,0,0,0,,What's cool about this LEGO block is that when you attach this blue block to the platform, it will enable the platform to move up and down periodically.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.07,0:40:27.42,中文,,0,0,0,,这个乐高积木的酷炫之处在于  当你将这个蓝色积木连接到平台上时  它将使平台能够周期性地上下移动
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.42,0:40:33.61,英文,,0,0,0,,So you don't have to write any code because the code that does this is already written for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.42,0:40:33.61,中文,,0,0,0,,所以你不需要编写任何代码  因为执行此操作的代码已经为你写好了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.61,0:40:38.85,英文,,0,0,0,,Now, even if you decide to write some sort of a code, the engine still abstracts a lot away from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.61,0:40:38.85,中文,,0,0,0,,现在  即使你决定编写某种代码  引擎仍然会为你抽象出很多东西
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.85,0:40:49.10,英文,,0,0,0,,In Build Your Own World, you need to come up with class definitions for Java classes, but in Unity, you can just define what are the sort of game objects that you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.85,0:40:49.10,中文,,0,0,0,,在“构建你自己的世界”中  你需要为Java类提出类定义  但在Unity中  你只需定义你想要的什么样的游戏对象
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.10,0:40:55.10,英文,,0,0,0,,and you can attach something called a script component to the game object you want to control.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.10,0:40:55.10,中文,,0,0,0,,然后将一个名为脚本组件的东西附加到你想要控制的游戏对象
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.10,0:41:05.01,英文,,0,0,0,,There are some rules for this script, and specifically it should inherit the MonoBehaviour and then override these two functions.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.10,0:41:05.01,中文,,0,0,0,,这个脚本有一些规则  特别是它应该继承MonoBehaviour  然后重写这两个函数
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.01,0:41:13.75,英文,,0,0,0,,You should define what the object should do when it's been initialized, and you should define what it should do at every frame.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.01,0:41:13.75,中文,,0,0,0,,你应该定义对象在初始化时应该做什么  以及它在每一帧应该做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.75,0:41:18.26,英文,,0,0,0,,And then you're just going to call those methods behind the scenes for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.75,0:41:18.26,中文,,0,0,0,,然后你只需要在幕后调用这些方法
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.26,0:41:20.26,英文,,0,0,0,,Now you might wonder, okay, what about scene transition?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.26,0:41:20.26,中文,,0,0,0,,现在你可能想知道  好吧  那场景转换呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.26,0:41:24.20,英文,,0,0,0,,We talked about scene transition like maybe a few minutes before.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.26,0:41:24.20,中文,,0,0,0,,我们几分钟前讨论过场景转换
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.20,0:41:26.72,英文,,0,0,0,,How does Unity handle that?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.20,0:41:26.72,中文,,0,0,0,,Unity 是如何处理场景转换的？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.72,0:41:35.38,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, Unity has a finite state machine that's running behind the scenes, and they actually provide you functions that you can use to change those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.72,0:41:35.38,中文,,0,0,0,,Unity 后台运行着一个有限状态机  它提供了一些函数来改变场景状态
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.38,0:41:39.92,英文,,0,0,0,,In the Unity editor, you can click on the File, New Scene to create a new scene for your game.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.38,0:41:39.92,中文,,0,0,0,,在 Unity 编辑器中  你可以点击“文件”  “新建场景”来为你的游戏创建一个新场景
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.92,0:41:47.41,英文,,0,0,0,,You can define what the game objects need to exist in that scene, and you can actually tell them, okay, here's what you should do when the scene starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.92,0:41:47.41,中文,,0,0,0,,你可以定义场景中需要存在哪些游戏对象  并告诉它们在场景开始时应该做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.41,0:41:55.27,英文,,0,0,0,,Maybe if this is your player, initialize the health to 100, set the score to zero or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.41,0:41:55.27,中文,,0,0,0,,例如  如果这是你的玩家  可以将生命值初始化为 100  将分数设置为零等等
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.27,0:42:02.52,英文,,0,0,0,,And then when you want to transition between the scenes, you just call this function called sceneManager.loadScene.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.27,0:42:02.52,中文,,0,0,0,,然后  当你想要在场景之间转换时  只需调用 sceneManager.loadScene 函数即可
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.52,0:42:04.65,英文,,0,0,0,,Now here's an example of a scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.52,0:42:04.65,中文,,0,0,0,,这是一个场景示例
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.65,0:42:05.35,英文,,0,0,0,,Here's another scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.65,0:42:05.35,中文,,0,0,0,,这是另一个场景
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.35,0:42:07.99,英文,,0,0,0,,Here's a lose scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.35,0:42:07.99,中文,,0,0,0,,这是一个失败场景
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.99,0:42:11.53,英文,,0,0,0,,And this is the code I've written for these two parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.99,0:42:11.53,中文,,0,0,0,,这是我为这两个部分编写的代码
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.53,0:42:17.54,英文,,0,0,0,,I actually opened up this Unity editor.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.53,0:42:17.54,中文,,0,0,0,,我打开了 Unity 编辑器
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.54,0:42:20.42,英文,,0,0,0,,So this is the camera object.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.54,0:42:20.42,中文,,0,0,0,,这是摄像机对象
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.42,0:42:22.83,英文,,0,0,0,,It has all the other stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.42,0:42:22.83,中文,,0,0,0,,它包含了所有其他内容
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.83,0:42:26.95,英文,,0,0,0,,You can see that there's a script that does the camera movement stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.83,0:42:26.95,中文,,0,0,0,,你可以看到有一个脚本负责摄像机的移动
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.95,0:42:29.71,英文,,0,0,0,,How do you make the camera follow the player?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.95,0:42:29.71,中文,,0,0,0,,如何让摄像机跟随玩家？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.71,0:42:31.31,英文,,0,0,0,,And then this is your player.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.71,0:42:31.31,中文,,0,0,0,,这是你的玩家
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.31,0:42:37.36,英文,,0,0,0,,These are just for the physics of the player, but then you also have a player controller script.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.31,0:42:37.36,中文,,0,0,0,,这些是玩家的物理属性  还有一个玩家控制器脚本
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.36,0:42:40.86,英文,,0,0,0,,And then you can just define what scenes you have here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.36,0:42:40.86,中文,,0,0,0,,你可以在这里定义场景
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.86,0:42:44.13,英文,,0,0,0,,And here is just the very bare bones like lose scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.86,0:42:44.13,中文,,0,0,0,,这是一个非常简单的失败场景
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.13,0:42:52.27,英文,,0,0,0,,You're going to define that you have like some sort of like a canvas to draw on and then you just say like you lose there.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.13,0:42:52.27,中文,,0,0,0,,你需要定义一个画布  然后在上面显示“游戏失败”之类的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.27,0:43:10.04,英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I can even like you know drag this player around to change his starting position and it's going to start a little bit off-centered, but that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.27,0:43:10.04,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯  我甚至可以拖动这个角色来改变他的起始位置  它会稍微偏离中心一点  就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.04,0:43:12.98,英文,,0,0,0,,There's still some general tips about writing good code.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.04,0:43:12.98,中文,,0,0,0,,关于编写好的代码还有一些通用技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.98,0:43:17.08,英文,,0,0,0,,For example, don't repeat yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.98,0:43:17.08,中文,,0,0,0,,例如  不要重复你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.08,0:43:23.63,英文,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't try to make different variants of an enemy, but you should just try to make one and inherit from that.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.08,0:43:23.63,中文,,0,0,0,,你不应该尝试制作敌人的不同变体  而应该尝试制作一个并从中继承
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.63,0:43:33.04,英文,,0,0,0,,If you have different versions of slimes, for example, you can just make three subclasses that all inherit from one superclass.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.63,0:43:33.04,中文,,0,0,0,,例如  如果你有不同版本的史莱姆  你可以只创建三个子类  它们都继承自一个超类
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.04,0:43:38.58,英文,,0,0,0,,You should also try to separate data from logic if you want to write games that are relatively big.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.04,0:43:38.58,中文,,0,0,0,,如果你想编写相对较大的游戏  你也应该尝试将数据与逻辑分离
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.58,0:43:42.02,英文,,0,0,0,,You maybe want to store them in a text file or somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.58,0:43:42.02,中文,,0,0,0,,你可能想将它们存储在文本文件或其他地方
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.02,0:43:48.36,英文,,0,0,0,,Just don't hard-code in the game because you're going to have a really long page of code that just has all the constants.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.02,0:43:48.36,中文,,0,0,0,,不要在游戏中硬编码  因为你将会有一个很长的代码页面  其中包含所有常量
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.36,0:43:52.38,英文,,0,0,0,,I think it might make your code a little bit bloated.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.36,0:43:52.38,中文,,0,0,0,,我认为这可能会使你的代码有点臃肿
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.38,0:44:01.82,英文,,0,0,0,,Also, you should learn to work with different types of assets, which are resources used in games, so like images, audio, or 3D models.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.38,0:44:01.82,中文,,0,0,0,,此外  你还应该学习使用不同类型的资产  这些资产是游戏中使用的资源  比如图像、音频或 3D 模型
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.82,0:44:05.30,英文,,0,0,0,,You also need to know some algorithms.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.82,0:44:05.30,中文,,0,0,0,,你还需要了解一些算法
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.30,0:44:10.36,英文,,0,0,0,,For example, A-Star pathfinding is actually used by zombies in Minecraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.30,0:44:10.36,中文,,0,0,0,,例如  《我的世界》中的僵尸实际上使用了 A* 寻路算法
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.36,0:44:20.70,英文,,0,0,0,,As a matter of fact, I think Project 3C has one feature that you can do, which is to implement some sort of pathfinding for enemies to chase, like the Avatar. Something similar to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.36,0:44:20.70,中文,,0,0,0,,事实上  我认为 Project 3C 有一个功能可以实现  那就是为敌人实现某种寻路算法来追逐  比如化身等类似的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.70,0:44:27.55,英文,,0,0,0,,Finally, don't repeat yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.70,0:44:27.55,中文,,0,0,0,,最后  不要重复你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.55,0:44:29.71,英文,,0,0,0,,We're not going to talk about game modding.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.55,0:44:29.71,中文,,0,0,0,,我们不打算谈论游戏模组
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.71,0:44:32.04,英文,,0,0,0,,It's another shift of gears.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.71,0:44:32.04,中文,,0,0,0,,这是另一个话题
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.04,0:44:35.70,英文,,0,0,0,,Let's say you don't want a dirty work of creating all like a brand new game.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.04,0:44:35.70,中文,,0,0,0,,假设你不想做创建全新游戏的脏活累活
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.70,0:44:38.24,英文,,0,0,0,,But then let's say I really love one of those existing games.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.70,0:44:38.24,中文,,0,0,0,,但是假设我真的很喜欢其中一个现有的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.24,0:44:41.57,英文,,0,0,0,,I want to just modify the things that are going on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.24,0:44:41.57,中文,,0,0,0,,我只想修改它上面发生的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.57,0:44:43.93,英文,,0,0,0,,And this is actually called game modding.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.57,0:44:43.93,中文,,0,0,0,,这实际上叫做游戏模组（game modding）
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.93,0:44:50.81,英文,,0,0,0,,It modifies the existing gameplay experience or just like adds new content to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.93,0:44:50.81,中文,,0,0,0,,它可以修改现有的游戏体验  或者像这样添加新的内容
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.81,0:44:52.62,英文,,0,0,0,,So one way is to add new levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.81,0:44:52.62,中文,,0,0,0,,所以一种方法是添加新的关卡
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.62,0:44:59.22,英文,,0,0,0,,This is a music game called OCE, where you just click on those circles and then those slide bars in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.62,0:44:59.22,中文,,0,0,0,,这是一个叫做 OCE 的音乐游戏  你只需要点击那些圆圈  然后及时地点击那些滑动条
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.22,0:45:06.41,英文,,0,0,0,,But then the game actually gives you a tool to add new beats according to a song that you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.22,0:45:06.41,中文,,0,0,0,,但然后游戏实际上给了你一个工具  可以根据你喜欢的歌曲添加新的节拍
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.41,0:45:14.75,英文,,0,0,0,,Now Super Mario games also have player-made level editors that you can drag and drop all the pipes, enemies, and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.41,0:45:14.75,中文,,0,0,0,,现在超级马里奥游戏也有玩家自制的关卡编辑器  你可以拖放所有的管道、敌人和其他东西
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.75,0:45:20.89,英文,,0,0,0,,Now you can also choose to add new content using code, and I'm going to show the Terraria code here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.75,0:45:20.89,中文,,0,0,0,,现在你也可以选择使用代码添加新的内容  我将在这里展示泰拉瑞亚（Terraria）的代码
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.89,0:45:23.95,英文,,0,0,0,,This is the mod I try to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.89,0:45:23.95,中文,,0,0,0,,这是我尝试做的模组
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.95,0:45:30.00,英文,,0,0,0,,So we're going to try to create a sword called the Sword of 61B in Terraria, and it's going to deal 61 damage,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.95,0:45:30.00,中文,,0,0,0,,所以我们要尝试在泰拉瑞亚中创建一个叫做 61B 之剑的剑  它将造成 61 点伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.00,0:45:36.00,英文,,0,0,0,,now less than 61 because enemy has some defense, and it's going to show this flavor text whenever you hit an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.00,0:45:36.00,中文,,0,0,0,,所以现在小于 61 点是因为敌人有一些防御  并且每当你击中敌人时  它将显示这段文字
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.00,0:45:38.17,英文,,0,0,0,,So how do I do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.00,0:45:38.17,中文,,0,0,0,,那么我该如何做呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.17,0:45:45.69,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm just gonna write a code that's like, you know, a sort 61B that extends like some sort of a class.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.17,0:45:45.69,中文,,0,0,0,,我只需要写一个代码  就像一个排序 61B 的类  它扩展了某种类型的类
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.69,0:45:48.39,英文,,0,0,0,,Now you might wonder, okay, how do I know it's these classes?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.69,0:45:48.39,中文,,0,0,0,,现在你可能会想  好吧  我怎么知道是这些类呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.39,0:45:50.44,英文,,0,0,0,,How do I know it's not something else?
